  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures Alicante charts 10-2G, 13-3, 13-4, and 13-5 from Jeppesen GSPRM 2017.<br>A pilot is expecting to follow either CALLES 1R (CLS 1R) or VALENCIA 1R (VLC 1R) STAR procedures. Which VOR approaches can the pilot follow afterwards?</p>",
